% ─── EXPLICIT SIZING ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@label sizing
    For manual control, \big through \Bigg set delimiter
    sizes explicitly.  Each step adds one row of height:

    $$ (a+b) \quad \big(a+b\big) \quad \Big(a+b\Big) \quad \bigg(a+b\bigg) \quad \Bigg(a+b\Bigg) $$
    $$ (\frac{a+b}{c+d}) \quad \big(\frac{a+b}{c+d}\big) \quad \Big(\frac{a+b}{c+d}\Big) \quad \bigg(\frac{a+b}{c+d}\bigg) \quad \Bigg(\frac{a+b}{c+d}\Bigg) $$

    $$ [x^2+y^2] \quad \big[x^2+y^2\big] \quad \Big[x^2+y^2\Big] \quad \bigg[x^2+y^2\bigg] \quad \Bigg[x^2+y^2\Bigg] $$
    $$ \left[ \frac{\sqrt{a^2+b^2}}{1+x} \right] \quad \Big[ \frac{\sqrt{a^2+b^2}}{1+x} \Big] $$

    $$ \{ a-b \} \quad \big\{ a-b \big\} \quad \Big\{ a-b \Big\} \quad \bigg\{ a-b \bigg\} \quad \Bigg\{ a-b \Bigg\} $$
    $$ \left\{ \frac{1}{2} + \sqrt[3]{z} \right\} \quad \Big\{ \frac{1}{2} + \sqrt[3]{z} \Big\} $$

    $$ |x| \quad \lvert x \rvert \quad \big| x+y \big| \quad \Big| x+y \Big| \quad \bigg| x+y \bigg| \quad \Bigg| x+y \Bigg| $$
    $$ \left| \frac{a+b}{\sqrt{1+u}} \right| \quad \Big| \frac{a+b}{\sqrt{1+u}} \Big| $$

    $$ \Vert v \Vert \quad \big\Vert v \big\Vert \quad \Big\Vert v \Big\Vert \quad \bigg\Vert v \bigg\Vert \quad \Bigg\Vert v \Bigg\Vert $$
    $$ \left\Vert \frac{\sqrt{m} + n}{1+q} \right\Vert $$

    $$ \lfloor x \rfloor \quad \big\lfloor x+y \big\rfloor \quad \Big\lfloor \frac{a+b}{c+d} \Big\rfloor \quad \bigg\lfloor \sqrt{1+u} \bigg\rfloor \quad \Bigg\lfloor \sqrt[3]{z} \Bigg\rfloor $$
    $$ \lceil x \rceil \quad \big\lceil x+y \big\rceil \quad \Big\lceil \frac{a+b}{c+d} \Big\rceil \quad \bigg\lceil \sqrt{1+u} \bigg\rceil \quad \Bigg\lceil \sqrt[5]{w} \Bigg\rceil $$

    $$ \left( \frac{a+b}{c+d} \right) \cdot \left[ \sqrt{1+u} \right] \cdot \left\{ \frac{x}{1+\sqrt[3]{z}} \right\} $$
    $$ \left| \frac{a+b}{\sqrt{1+u}} \right| \quad \left\Vert \frac{x^2+y^2}{1+t} \right\Vert \quad \left\lceil \frac{m+n}{p+q} \right\rceil \quad \left\lfloor \sqrt{1+v} \right\rfloor $$

    $$ \left| \Bigg( \frac{\sqrt{a^2+b^2}}{1+\sqrt[3]{z}} \Bigg) \right| \quad \left\lceil \big[ \frac{x+y}{\sqrt{1+u}} \big] \right\rceil \quad \left\lfloor \{ \frac{p}{q} \} \right\rfloor $$

    Standalone one-sided delimiters use \cmd{bigl}/\cmd{bigr}
    (and \cmd{Bigl}/\cmd{Bigr}, \cmd{biggl}/\cmd{biggr}, \cmd{Biggl}/\cmd{Biggr}).
    Useful for evaluation bars:

    $$ f(x)\bigr|_{x=0} \quad \frac{d}{dx}f(x)\biggr|_{x=0} $$
@end

