% ─── RELATIONS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@label relations
    Beyond equals, Hyades supports the full set of relational
    operators:

    $$ a \neq b $$
    $$ a \leq b $$
    $$ a \geq b $$
    $$ a \ll b $$
    $$ a \gg b $$
    $$ a \approx b $$
    $$ a \equiv b $$
    $$ a \sim b $$
    $$ a \propto b $$
    $$ a \prec b \quad a \succ b $$
    $$ a \preceq b \quad a \succeq b $$

    The \cmd{not} prefix negates a relation:

    $$ a \not= b \quad x \not\in A \quad a \not\leq b $$
    $$ a \not\equiv b \quad A \not\subset B \quad \not\exists x $$
@end

@cassilda: relations
