│  
│                                      𝐴 ∩ 𝐵
│  
│                                      𝐴 ∖ 𝐵
│  
│                                        ∅

% ─── LOGIC ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@label logic
    Quantifiers, connectives, and arrows:

    $$ \forall x \in \mathbb{R} $$
    $$ \exists x $$
    $$ \neg p $$
    $$ p \land q $$
    $$ p \lor q $$
    $$ p \implies q $$
    $$ p \iff q $$
    $$ \top \quad \bot $$
    $$ \therefore \quad \because $$
@end

