% ─── ARROWS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@label arrows
    Arrows come in many forms:

    $$ \rightarrow \quad \leftarrow \quad \leftrightarrow $$
    $$ \Rightarrow \quad \Leftarrow \quad \Leftrightarrow $$
    $$ \mapsto \quad \longmapsto $$
    $$ \hookrightarrow \quad \hookleftarrow $$
    $$ \uparrow \quad \downarrow \quad \updownarrow $$
    $$ \nearrow \quad \searrow \quad \nwarrow \quad \swarrow $$

    Extensible arrows carry a label that stretches the arrow:

    $$ A \xrightarrow{f} B \xleftarrow{g} C $$
@end

