% ─── TEXT IN MATH ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@label text_in_math
    \cmd{text} inserts upright text inside math mode.
    Useful for conditions and labels:

    $$ x = 0 \text{ if } y > 0 $$
    $$ f(x) \text{ for all } x \in \mathbb{R} $$
@end

@cassilda: text_in_math
