│                                  𝑥 = 0 if 𝑦 > 0
│  
│                                𝑓(𝑥) for all 𝑥 ∈ ℝ

% ─── ACCENTS AND DECORATIONS ─────────────────────────────────────────────

@label accents
    Single-character accents attach to the next symbol:

    $$ \hat{x} \quad \bar{x} \quad \tilde{x} \quad \vec{x} $$
    $$ \dot{x} \quad \ddot{x} $$
    $$ \acute{x} \quad \grave{x} \quad \breve{x} \quad \check{x} $$

    Wide accents span multiple characters:

    $$ \widehat{xyz}\quad \widetilde{xyz}\quad \overline{xyz}\quad \underline{xyz}
       \quad\overrightarrow{AB}
       \quad\overleftarrow{AB} $$
@end

@cassilda: accents
│  Single-character accents attach to the next symbol:
│  
│                                 𝑥̂    𝑥̄    𝑥̃    𝑥⃗
│  
│                                      𝑥̇    𝑥̈
│  
│                                 𝑥́    𝑥̀    𝑥̆    𝑥̌
│  
│  Wide accents span multiple characters:
│  
│                       ╱⎺╲    ╱∼╲    ⎽⎽⎽           ─→    ←─
│                       𝑥𝑦𝑧    𝑥𝑦𝑧    𝑥𝑦𝑧    𝑥𝑦𝑧    𝐴𝐵    𝐴𝐵
│                                            ───

% ─── OVERBRACE AND UNDERBRACE ────────────────────────────────────────────

@label braces
    \cmd{overbrace} and \cmd{underbrace} draw horizontal brackets above
    or below content, with an optional centered label:

    $$ \overbrace{a + b + c}^{3 \text{ terms}} $$

    $$ \underbrace{x_1 + x_2 + \cdots + x_n}_{n \text{ terms}} $$

    Braces nest naturally:

    $$ \overbrace{\underbrace{a + b}_{2} + c}^{3} $$

    $$ \underbrace{\overbrace{a + b}^{x} + \overbrace{c + d}^{y}}_{z} $$

    They also work inside larger expressions:

    $$ \sum_{i=1}^{n} \underbrace{a_i \cdot b_i}_\text{dot product} $$
@end

@cassilda: braces
│  \𝑜𝑣𝑒𝑟𝑏𝑟𝑎𝑐𝑒 and  \𝑢𝑛𝑑𝑒𝑟𝑏𝑟𝑎𝑐𝑒 draw horizontal  brackets above or below  content,
│  with an optional centered label:
│  
│                                     3 terms
│                                    ╭───┴───╮
│                                    𝑎 + 𝑏 + 𝑐
│  
│                                 𝑥  + 𝑥  + ⋯ + 𝑥
│                                  1    2        𝑛
│                                 ╰───────┬──────╯
│                                     𝑛 terms
│  
│  Braces nest naturally:
│  
