% ─── PRODUCTS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@label products
    \cmd{prod} gives the product symbol. \cmd{Prod}/\cmd{PROD} for larger variants:

    $$ \prod_{i=1}^{n} x_i $$
    $$ \Prod_{i=1}^{n} x_i\quad
       \PROD_{i=1}^{n} x_i $$

    
    $$ \Prod_{i=1}^{n} \left( \sqrt{\frac{\left(\frac{x}{y}\right)}{1+\sqrt[3]{z}}} \right) \quad
       \Prod^{m} \left( \frac{\sqrt{a^2+b^2}}{\left( \frac{c}{d} \right)} \right)$$

    ASCII version:

    \setunicode{false}

    $$ \Prod_{i=1}^{n} \left( \sqrt{\frac{\left(\frac{x}{y}\right)}{1+\sqrt[3]{z}}} \right) \quad
       \Prod^{m} \left( \frac{\sqrt{a^2+b^2}}{\left( \frac{c}{d} \right)} \right)$$
@end

