% ─── MULTIPLE AND CONTOUR INTEGRALS ──────────────────────────────────────

@label multi_integrals
    Double and triple integrals, contour integrals:

    $$ \iint f(x,y) \, dx\,dy $$
    $$ \iiint f(x,y,z) \, dx\,dy\,dz $$
    $$ \oint_C f(z) \, dz $$
    $$ \oiint_S \mathbf{F} \cdot d\mathbf{S} $$

    Bigger variants are available as well using the same naming notation
    as usual:

    $$ \Iint \IINT \Iiint \IIINT \Oint \OINT \Oiint \OIINT $$
    
    Double integral over region $R$:
    $$ \iint_R f(x,y)\,dA = \int_a^b \int_{g_1(x)}^{g_2(x)} f(x,y)\,dy\,dx $$

    Green's theorem:

    $$\oint_C \mathbf{F} \cdot d\mathbf{r} =
      \iint_D \left(\frac{\partial Q}{\partial x} - \frac{\partial P}{\partial y}\right) dA$$
@end

