% ─── CALCULUS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@label calculus
    Derivatives, partial derivatives, differential operators:

    $$ \frac{dy}{dx}\quad
       \frac{d^2y}{dx^2}\quad
       \frac{\partial f}{\partial x}\quad
       \frac{\partial^2 f}{\partial x \partial y} $$

    Gradient and Laplacian:

    $$ \nabla f $$
    $$ \nabla \cdot \mathbf{F} $$
    $$ \nabla \times \mathbf{F} $$
    $$ \nabla^2 f $$
@end

