% ─── MATRICES ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@label matrices
    Six matrix types provide different delimiters.  Ampersand
    separates columns, double-backslash separates rows:

    $$ \pmatrix{a & b \\ c & d} + \bmatrix{a & b \\ c & d} + \Bmatrix{a & b \\ c & d} $$
    $$ \vmatrix{a & b \\ c & d} + \Vmatrix{a & b \\ c & d}$$
    $$ \matrix{a & b \\ c & d} $$
@end

