% ─── SPACING ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@label spacing
    Explicit spacing commands for fine control.  Shown here
    from smallest to largest -- negative, thin, medium, thick,
    quad (1em), and double-quad (2em):

    $$ a \! b $$
    $$ a \, b $$
    $$ a \: b $$
    $$ a \; b $$
    $$ a \quad b $$
    $$ a \qquad b $$

    Common use: thin space before dx in integrals:

    $$ \int f(x) \, dx $$
@end

