% ─── PHANTOM ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@label phantom
    \cmd{phantom} creates invisible whitespace with the same
    dimensions as its content.  Useful for alignment tricks:

    $$ a + \phantom{xyz} + c $$
@end

@cassilda: phantom
│  \𝑝ℎ𝑎𝑛𝑡𝑜𝑚 creates invisible whitespace with the same dimensions as its content.
