% ─── TAG ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@label tag
    \cmd{tag} appends a numbered equation tag:

    $$ E = mc^2 \tag{1} $$

    Tags also work on \cmd{aligned} blocks.  The tag is
    right-justified and vertically centered:

    $$\aligned{
        f(x) &= x^2 + 2x + 1 \\
             &= (x + 1)^2
    } \tag{7}$$
@end

